BT /F1 8 Tf 66 631 Td (Category-affinity popularity: Provides robust candidates for sparse users.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 66 616 Td (Global popularity fallback: Prevents empty or brittle candidate sets.) Tj ET
